Usage: editChangeStatus [-help] [<shield_net_name>] [-nets <net>+]
                        -to {ROUTED FIXED COVER SHIELD NOSHIELD}

-help                 # Prints out the command usage
<shield_net_name>     # the net to be shielded by the selected wire or belong
                      # to the net specified by -nets (string, optional)
-nets <net>+          # Specifies the name of the nets to be change the status.
                      # ((net)+, optional)
-to {ROUTED FIXED COVER SHIELD NOSHIELD}
                      # status
                      # (enum, required)